107
00:07:29,980 --> 00:07:31,980
You come to my place first thing in the morning to force me.

108
00:07:31,980 --> 00:07:33,960
Are you considering me your brother?

109
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:38,770
I don't care if you acknowledge it or not, but I definitely think of you as a brother.

110
00:07:38,770 --> 00:07:41,030
