111
00:07:41,030 --> 00:07:44,110
I came here today because of this basket of eggs.

112
00:07:46,590 --> 00:07:49,130
A client of mine gave me this basket of eggs.

113
00:07:49,130 --> 00:07:51,690
Originally, he had the eggs, but couldn't sell them.

114
00:07:51,690 --> 00:07:55,060
He only makes a few thousand bucks a month.

115
00:07:55,060 --> 00:07:59,430
But now, because he has my Fast's rural logistics system,

116
00:07:59,430 --> 00:08:02,700
