138
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:20,370
Cloud computing logistics.

139
00:09:20,370 --> 00:09:22,460
"Cloud computing logistics."

140
00:09:24,760 --> 00:09:28,470
- So am I a part of your plans?
- What a question!

141
00:09:28,470 --> 00:09:31,690
Do you think I'll let you eat this basket of eggs for free?

142
00:09:31,700 --> 00:09:33,870
Okay.

143
00:09:33,870 --> 00:09:37,350
- We're brothers now.
- We already were.

144
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:41,810
[Beijing Jia An Building]

145
00:09:41,810 --> 00:09:43,440
Director Zhou.

146
00:09:49,400 --> 00:09:53,000
Instead of waiting for you to come, I may as well wait for you here.

147
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:54,560
Come!

148
00:09:58,220 --> 00:09:59,650
Come!

149
