150
00:10:04,070 --> 00:10:07,710
My apology, Director Zhou! I've already decided to sign a contract with Director Luo.

151
00:10:10,620 --> 00:10:14,360
Then... President Guo, you spending time waiting for me here,

152
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:16,470
