270
00:17:52,940 --> 00:17:57,320
Grandma, what did you forget to take with you again?

271
00:18:02,640 --> 00:18:05,060
I was just about to look for you.

272
00:18:05,060 --> 00:18:06,850
What's the matter?

273
00:18:10,760 --> 00:18:14,490
I installed an app on my grandma's phone to prevent her from going missing.

274
00:18:14,490 --> 00:18:17,900
It needs two emergency contacts.

275
00:18:20,990 --> 00:18:23,020
I know.

276
00:18:23,020 --> 00:18:25,050
The other one is me.

277
00:19:10,700 --> 00:19:12,560
In 1967,

278
00:19:12,560 --> 00:19:17,110
Cellist Jacqueline du Pré married the pianist and conductor, Daniel Barenboim.

279
00:19:17,110 --> 00:19:19,900
It's a great love story from the classical music world.

280
00:19:24,490 --> 00:19:29,370
This is one of the best cello performances that I've ever heard.

281
00:19:39,630 --> 00:19:41,790
I'm giving you this album.

282
00:19:51,030 --> 00:19:56,150
I don't think you've ever used your vinyl player before.

283
00:19:56,150 --> 00:19:58,320
No, I haven't.

284
00:20:12,280 --> 00:20:14,350
Why are you leaving suddenly?

285
00:20:17,010 --> 00:20:18,760
It's because of you.

286
00:20:19,790 --> 00:20:21,650
"Because of me?"

287
00:20:23,890 --> 00:20:27,020
Every knife you cut sees blood. Didn't you know?

288
00:20:27,020 --> 00:20:29,050
I can't pretend that I have no feelings, can I?

289
00:20:29,050 --> 00:20:31,550
I can only wipe the blood on my body clean

290
00:20:31,550 --> 00:20:34,170
- and bury it—
- Zhuo Rui, I don't want to hear you ramble.

291
00:20:38,670 --> 00:20:41,200
I want to open up a new battlefield.

292
00:20:41,200 --> 00:20:42,730
I'm leaving for Northwest China

293
00:20:42,730 --> 00:20:45,410
to start from the bottom with the small-to-mid sized businesses.

294
00:21:05,340 --> 00:21:06,940
Zhou Rui,

295
00:21:09,310 --> 00:21:13,950
from this moment on, don't look at me or interrupt me while I'm talking.

296
00:21:13,950 --> 00:21:16,230
I'm afraid I'll change my mind.

297
00:21:28,620 --> 00:21:31,310
When I mentioned breaking up before,

298
00:21:31,310 --> 00:21:34,240
I was emotional. Did you know?

299
00:21:35,670 --> 00:21:37,930
Every time after I get emotional,

300
00:21:37,930 --> 00:21:40,450
I would regret that I hurled those hurtful words to you.

301
00:21:42,610 --> 00:21:45,550
But actually, you're in my heart.

302
00:21:45,550 --> 00:21:47,350
Do you know that?

303
00:21:54,310 --> 00:21:56,860
I don't want to love many people.

304
00:21:57,640 --> 00:22:00,120
I also don't want to love many times.

305
00:22:00,790 --> 00:22:02,670
I only want to know,

306
00:22:02,670 --> 00:22:07,230
if you must have someone in your future plans, why can't that person be me?

307
00:22:07,230 --> 00:22:09,430
- Luo Jia—
- Don't interrupt!

308
00:22:09,430 --> 00:22:11,600
I have to interrupt.

309
00:22:12,970 --> 00:22:15,220
You're in my heart.

310
00:22:18,180 --> 00:22:21,790
It's only outside of your work and during leisure time, isn't it?

311
00:22:21,790 --> 00:22:24,160
Aren't all men like this?

312
00:22:31,130 --> 00:22:33,750
However, you don't have much free time.

313
00:22:33,750 --> 00:22:36,800
- Luo Jia—
- I told you not to interrupt me.

314
00:22:40,050 --> 00:22:41,720
Zhou Rui,

315
00:22:42,610 --> 00:22:45,340
I know you already tried your best.

316
00:22:47,400 --> 00:22:50,050
However, what I want,

317
00:22:50,050 --> 00:22:53,070
you still can't give it to me.

318
00:22:57,150 --> 00:23:00,640
It's because neither of us will change for the other.

319
00:23:03,350 --> 00:23:05,990
We loved each other before.

320
00:23:06,810 --> 00:23:08,800
We've had each other in our hearts before.

321
00:23:08,800 --> 00:23:10,940
To be honest,

322
00:23:10,940 --> 00:23:12,560
that's enough...

323
00:23:16,140 --> 00:23:18,060
Therefore,

324
00:23:20,200 --> 00:23:22,230
I want to tell you,

325
00:23:26,230 --> 00:23:28,960
let's break up this time for real.

