00:24:26,170 --> 00:24:28,590
Director Zhou!

338
00:24:30,370 --> 00:24:33,250
- Are you getting use to blocking my car?
- Director Zhou.

339
00:24:33,250 --> 00:24:36,450
Don't you think something good happens whenever I stop your car?

340
00:24:36,450 --> 00:24:38,260
Something good? Such as?

341
00:24:38,260 --> 00:24:40,970
Such as, look behind you!

342
00:24:50,760 --> 00:24:52,980
Boss!

343
00:25:05,480 --> 00:25:11,450
[Penalty Notification]
[Our company's employee, Zhou Rui, Sales Director, has disobeyed the company's decision, and is now punished with leave without pay.]

344
00:25:11,450 --> 00:25:14,740
Leave without pay

345
00:25:14,740 --> 00:25:16,740
is the best that I can do for you.

346
00:25:17,990 --> 00:25:19,940
Hi!

347
00:25:27,790 --> 00:25:29,700
Mister, here.

348
00:25:29,700 --> 00:25:32,220
For you! You've worked hard.

349
00:25:32,220 --> 00:25:34,390
You've worked hard, Mister.

350
00:25:38,070 --> 00:25:40,400
Who's seen the bottled waters?

351
00:25:40,400 --> 00:25:43,690
Fang Wei, hyou seen those bottled waters?

352
00:25:44,230 --> 00:25:45,960
You must've forgotten it.

353
00:25:56,220 --> 00:25:58,240
Twist it! Twist the legs counterclockwise.

354
00:25:58,240 --> 00:26:00,360
Everyone, come over here for a bit!

355
00:26:02,130 --> 00:26:04,450
This is the local village officer that I previously mentioned to you all before.

356
00:26:04,450 --> 00:26:06,900
He's called Shi Peng Fei who can help us resolve many local problems.

357
00:26:06,900 --> 00:26:08,750
- This is Old Cao.
- I'm Cao Tian You.

358
00:26:08,750 --> 00:26:11,120
- Call me Xiao Shi.
- Fang Wei. Bei Yao Yao.
- Hello.

359
00:26:11,120 --> 00:26:13,070
- Hello.
- Hello. Hello!
- Sit. Sit. Have a seat!

360
00:26:13,070 --> 00:26:15,070
Come, come, come!

361
00:26:16,250 --> 00:26:18,310
I'll go to get something to eat first.

362
00:26:18,310 --> 00:26:20,240
- Sit down first!
- Drink whatever you want. Open it and drink it.

363
00:26:20,240 --> 00:26:21,770
- Help me hold it for a bit.
- Okay.

364
00:26:22,700 --> 00:26:24,890
You Shi guy, where are you running to?

365
00:26:24,890 --> 00:26:28,730
- I just don't believe your four wheels can run faster than my four hoofs.
- No, wait! What are you doing?

366
00:26:28,730 --> 00:26:30,360
- What do you mean "what am I doing?"
- They are guests. What are you doing?

367
00:26:30,360 --> 00:26:32,660
- What guests?
- What are you doing?

368
00:26:32,660 --> 00:26:34,630
I lost my cattle again!

369
00:26:34,630 --> 00:26:36,870
- I know that.
- If you know, why did you run away and didn't help me search for it?

370
00:26:36,870 --> 00:26:39,090
- What's going on?
- He lost his cattle.

371
00:26:39,090 --> 00:26:40,950
Lost his cattle?

372
00:26:41,560 --> 00:26:44,400
Come with me to search for the cattle!

373
00:26:48,190 --> 00:26:50,580
- It tastes good.
- Boss.

374
00:26:50,580 --> 00:26:52,130
Thanks.

375
00:26:54,270 --> 00:26:55,620
- Director Zhou,
- Go over there and get us something to eat.

376
00:26:55,620 --> 00:26:57,590
be the judge for us!

377
00:26:57,590 --> 00:26:59,660
I pleaded with Hasi Bagen

378
00:26:59,660 --> 00:27:01,480
not to contract out the ranch.

379
00:27:01,480 --> 00:27:04,580
Those city people will occupy your land and won't do any work.

380
00:27:04,580 --> 00:27:06,720
If you... you've done ranching half your lifetime,

381
00:27:06,720 --> 00:27:09,960
then you go to work in the city, what kind of work can you do?

382
00:27:09,960 --> 00:27:12,860
What kind of money can you make, right?

383
00:27:12,860 --> 00:27:15,020
Shi guy, what money can you talk about with me?

384
00:27:15,020 --> 00:27:17,290
You made us tear down our fences,

385
00:27:17,290 --> 00:27:21,150
and put some rings on the cattle saying it's high-tech, and what's the result?

386
00:27:21,150 --> 00:27:22,950
Don't you know how many cattle have been lost?

387
00:27:22,950 --> 00:27:25,370
I-I already promised you.

388
00:27:25,370 --> 00:27:28,660
I'll find each and every one of your cattle for you.

389
00:27:28,660 --> 00:27:30,300
If they aren't found, I'll compensate you.

390
00:27:30,300 --> 00:27:31,590
You'll compensate me?

391
00:27:31,590 --> 00:27:33,170
- What are you going to compensate me with?
- Eat that.

392
00:27:33,170 --> 00:27:36,920
- Use money to compensate.
- Do I look like I need money?

393
00:27:36,920 --> 00:27:39,540
We've been ranching for several generations.

394
00:27:39,540 --> 00:27:41,890
We don't need money! I'm bored with it.

395
00:27:41,890 --> 00:27:44,160
Anyway, I-I'm telling you,

396
00:27:44,160 --> 00:27:46,960
you can't contract out the ranch to the city people.

397
00:27:46,960 --> 00:27:50,090
They will ruin the legacy of several decades of ranching culture.

398
00:27:50,090 --> 00:27:52,120
Xiao Shi, I have a general idea...

399
00:27:52,120 --> 00:27:53,830
A general...

400
00:27:53,830 --> 00:27:56,070
I have a general understanding about your standpoint.

401
00:27:56,070 --> 00:27:59,400
But can you tell me exactly what happened?

402
00:27:59,890 --> 00:28:01,270
You say it!

403
00:28:01,270 --> 00:28:03,180
You say it.

404
00:28:03,180 --> 00:28:05,220
Y-You say it!

405
00:28:07,480 --> 00:28:09,660
He tore down our fences.

406
00:28:09,660 --> 00:28:12,420
He insisted on putting on some rings on our cattle.

407
00:28:12,420 --> 00:28:14,930
Some high-tech rings, right?

408
00:28:14,930 --> 00:28:18,500
- In the end, we lost the cattle.
- Electronic collar.

409
00:28:18,960 --> 00:28:22,500
- How is the signal transmitted?
- By radio transmission.

410
00:28:22,500 --> 00:28:25,980
The signal machine is in my car, but the signal keeps disconnecting.

411
00:28:25,980 --> 00:28:27,890
Just think! I studied liberal arts.

412
00:28:27,890 --> 00:28:30,760
- Another cup.
- I don't know how to tinker with that machine sometimes.

413
00:28:30,760 --> 00:28:33,870
Even when I drive the car in front of the cattle, the machine still doesn't do anything.

414
00:28:33,870 --> 00:28:37,010
I get it. I get it!

415
00:28:37,580 --> 00:28:40,380
The cattle are lost, then you're in trouble.

416
00:28:40,380 --> 00:28:44,410
It's trouble to him, but it's a loss to us.

417
00:28:44,410 --> 00:28:46,070
Each ox costs over ten thousand yuan.

418
00:28:46,070 --> 00:28:49,630
You want to compensate? Can you afford to?

419
00:28:53,630 --> 00:28:57,830
- Director Zhou, let's not talk about cloud computing today.
- Okay.

420
00:28:57,830 --> 00:29:02,440
I need to drive the car to help him search for the cattle right now.

421
00:29:02,440 --> 00:29:04,160
As for the proposal for Sky and Earth,

422
00:29:04,160 --> 00:29:06,090
I won't give it to you for now.

423
00:29:06,090 --> 00:29:09,270
I'll think of a solution to help you solve your problem.

424
00:29:09,270 --> 00:29:11,000
Th-Thank you, Director Zhou.

425
00:29:11,000 --> 00:29:12,660
I'm leaving then.

426
00:29:15,960 --> 00:29:19,090
Brother, what's your name?

427
00:29:19,730 --> 00:29:21,080
Hasi Bagen.

428
00:29:21,080 --> 00:29:22,460
Come!

429
00:29:24,770 --> 00:29:27,560
Jieke Faster Company.

430
00:29:27,560 --> 00:29:29,740
I'll help you find the cattle.

431
00:29:49,040 --> 00:29:51,920
The cattle are really difficult to find.

432
00:29:51,920 --> 00:29:53,710
The radio transmission has problems.

433
00:29:53,710 --> 00:29:55,440
Using radio transmissi is too weak.

434
00:29:55,440 --> 00:29:58,170
I think it's because of the Beidou.
 (TN: Beidou Navigation Satellite System)

435
00:30:05,670 --> 00:30:07,970
- Go!
- Here!

436
00:30:07,970 --> 00:30:09,330
- You're impressive, Mr. Lin.
- Let me try!

437
00:30:09,330 --> 00:30:11,250
- Okay.
- Try it.

438
00:30:16,150 --> 00:30:19,920
Please tell President Lin that I'm here.

439
00:30:23,260 --> 00:30:24,550
- President Lin,
- What?

440
00:30:24,550 --> 00:30:26,280
there's a Mr. Wei outside.

441
00:30:26,280 --> 00:30:28,880
- He said he has an appointment with you.
- I got it.

442
00:30:28,880 --> 00:30:32,200
- Okay. Continue to play first! I'll go and see.
- Go ahead.

443
00:30:32,940 --> 00:30:34,600
Open your mouth! Go in.

444
00:30:44,440 --> 00:30:46,020
President Lin.

445
00:30:47,640 --> 00:30:50,240
You're 15 minutes late.

446
00:30:51,390 --> 00:30:54,720
Do you know that in 15 minutes,

447
00:30:54,720 --> 00:30:57,420
- you can negotiate a neither too big nor too small deal?
- I'm sorry.

448
00:30:57,420 --> 00:30:59,790
I had to take care of some things at home.

449
00:31:04,440 --> 00:31:07,000
Why do you smell like the hospital?

450
00:31:07,790 --> 00:31:11,320
- President Lin, last time you said—
- Change your bad habits!

451
00:31:11,320 --> 00:31:13,690
Don't just get straight to the point.

452
00:31:13,690 --> 00:31:15,880
That's all I know to do.

453
00:31:16,500 --> 00:31:19,900
Our suppliers are putting off supplying our materials and now they're raising their prices.

454
00:31:19,900 --> 00:31:23,190
These are signs that Americans give off before they they cut off supply.

455
00:31:23,190 --> 00:31:28,130
Director Wei, the Americans have talked about cutting off the Chinese's chip supply for many years now.

456
00:31:28,130 --> 00:31:32,440
Whether people believe it or not, and even if they really do cut us off,

457
00:31:32,440 --> 00:31:35,260
then Jieke still won't be the only one who'll have problems.

458
00:31:35,260 --> 00:31:39,140
Internet companies throughout China will all be affected.

459
00:31:39,140 --> 00:31:41,910
You're a salesman.

460
00:31:42,680 --> 00:31:44,790
Do you have to be that worried?

461
00:31:51,800 --> 00:31:53,590
Okay.

462
00:31:55,280 --> 00:31:57,460
Let me talk about another matter then.

463
00:31:57,460 --> 00:32:01,790
O&T's Chairman Liu, Liu Feng, is also interested in Jieke.

464
00:32:01,790 --> 00:32:05,240
You should know about this, shouldn't you?

465
00:32:07,060 --> 00:32:09,320
If this matter

466
00:32:09,920 --> 00:32:14,260
is true, it still can't be said with certainty if it's a blessing or a curse.

467
00:32:14,980 --> 00:32:18,570
But for you, it's definitely not a blessing.

468
00:32:28,720 --> 00:32:31,430
To show sincerity,

469
00:32:31,950 --> 00:32:35,920
I've already sent a client's information to Director Luo last time.

470
00:32:37,610 --> 00:32:41,010
In here, it's everything.

471
00:32:41,770 --> 00:32:45,110
Is the agreement between us still valid?

472
00:32:45,700 --> 00:32:47,840
Of course, it's still valid.

473
00:33:01,620 --> 00:33:04,060
Come on, President Lin!

474
00:33:23,490 --> 00:33:25,100
- Bye-bye.
- Goodbye!
- Bye-bye!

475
00:33:25,100 --> 00:33:27,110
- Bye bye!
- Thank you!
- Thanks!

476
00:33:27,110 --> 00:33:29,390
Come back again next time, Brother!

477
00:33:32,290 --> 00:33:34,380
What's the matter, Big Guy?

478
00:33:34,380 --> 00:33:38,370
We should at least, give a gift on the first meeting upon coming here.

479
00:33:39,500 --> 00:33:42,970
Are you trying to be a do gooder again and save people from disaster?

480
00:33:45,240 --> 00:33:47,290
Bei Yao Yao.

481
00:33:47,290 --> 00:33:50,340
A free drone! You take care of it.

482
00:33:50,920 --> 00:33:53,130
- Okay.
- Fang Wei!

483
00:33:53,130 --> 00:33:55,330
I know what I need to do.

484
00:34:06,130 --> 00:34:08,500
Hello, this is Zhong Lian Technology Company, is it?

485
00:34:09,210 --> 00:34:12,220
I am O&T's Director Zhao's friend.

486
00:34:12,220 --> 00:34:14,320
Right, Zhao Lan.

487
00:34:15,410 --> 00:34:17,760
- Hello!
- We want to request the approximate location

488
00:34:17,760 --> 00:34:20,660
- Chairman Wang.
- of something that uses a radio transmitter.

489
00:34:20,660 --> 00:34:23,150
- Hello, hello!
- Cattle. It's cattle.

490
00:34:23,150 --> 00:34:25,610
Have you received the beef jerky I sent you?

491
00:34:25,610 --> 00:34:28,000
